## Actualizar halcon

```bash
halcon update
```

---

## Desinstalar

```bash
# macOS / Linux
rm ~/.local/bin/halcon
rm -rf ~/.halcon      # elimina configuración y base de datos local

# Windows
Remove-Item "$env:USERPROFILE\.local\bin\halcon.exe"
Remove-Item -Recurse "$env:USERPROFILE\.halcon"
```

